profile: Classic Rock Garden Ornaments is a family-owned retail/wholesale store in Victoria, BC, Canada.  We specialize in fountains of all kinds: outdoor fountains, wall fountains, estate fountains, commercial fountains, residential fountains, patio fountains, etc.  We carry a full line of garden ornaments: bird baths, statues, outdoor concrete tables and benches, plaques and stepping stones, animals, Asian lanterns and planters/containers.
